lz4compress
===========

lz4compress is a command line tool for compressing files using lz4 algorithm.
For more information run lz4compress --help.

List of 3rd party libraries used:
  - lz4 (https://code.google.com/p/lz4/);
  - TCLAP (http://tclap.sourceforge.net/).

Use CMake to generate the MSVS solution:
  mkdir build
  cd build
  cmake <path to lz4compress source directory>

Currently only MSVS2012+ is supported (tr2 extensions used).
